markdownRemark.html: This is a charming nine-hole golf course, located near Los Aqueros. It's is a relatively new course with a challenging design, especially when starting with a par 3 downhill with OB beyond and water in play. You can easily walk this course, however buggies are available for those who need it. Throughout the course you can enjoy wonderful views of the sea.

frontmatter.title: Club de Golf El Higueral
frontmatter.description: Club de Golf El Higueral - This is a charming nine-hole golf course, located in the Benahavis area just across the road from Los Arqueros Golf. It's is a relatively new course with a challenging design, especially when starting with a par 3 downhill with OB beyond and water in play. You can easily walk this course, however buggies are available for those who need it. Throughout the course you can enjoy wonderful views of the sea.
frontmatter.address: Urb. Capanes Golf. Km. 3,7 Ctra. de Benahavís,  29679 Benahavís, Marbella, Malaga, Spain
frontmatter.price: Highest green fee weekdays 39.00 euros, Highest green fee weekends 39.00 euros
